>> help mktrkrng

  function mktrkrng(year_base, infile, outfile, dxy, halfwidth);
  Make Alongtrack Time Ranges
 
  Generate a set of time ranges to be used by adcpsect
  for extracting velocities, typically for vector plotting.
  Ranges are generated at uniform along-track intervals,
  based on a smoothed version of the ship's velocity from
  the output of smoothr.
 
  yearbase: 4-digit year.
  infile: made up of lines from *.sm (smoothr output)
  outfile will have time ranges
  dxy is the interval in km
  (optional) halfwidth is the half width of the ship
      velocity smoothing blackman filter, in units of adcp
      ensembles.  Default is 6.
 
  EF Sun  99/02/28
 

